description:
PmMeasurementCapabilities: Table recording the performance measurement capabilities of cells in a radio access network.

- dateTime: Timestamp of the record.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographic area.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell.
- Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
- Id3:  Redundant identifier (always '1' in sample data).
- Id4: Redundant identifier (always '1' in sample data).
- vsDataType:  Data type identifier.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.maxNoOfThresholdJobs: Maximum number of threshold jobs supported.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.maxNoOfMeasurementJobs: Maximum number of measurement jobs supported.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.realTimeJobSupport: Boolean indicating real-time job support.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.alignedReportingPeriod: Boolean indicating support for aligned reporting periods.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.supportedRopPeriods: Supported reporting periods for ROP (Reporting on Performance).
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.fileLocation: Location of PM (Performance Monitoring) files.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.maxNoOfPmFiles: Maximum number of PM files supported.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.jobPrioritizationSupport: Boolean indicating job prioritization support.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.fileRPSupported: Boolean indicating file-based reporting support.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.thresholdJobSupport: Boolean indicating threshold job support.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.ropFilenameTimestamp: Timestamp format in ROP filenames.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.jobGroupingSupport: Boolean indicating job grouping support.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.maxNoOfMeasurements: Maximum number of measurements supported.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.maxNoOfJobs: Maximum number of jobs supported.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.supportedMeasJobGps: Supported GPS intervals for measurement jobs.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.pmMeasurementCapabilitiesId: Unique identifier for the capabilities record.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.maxNoOfRealtimeJobs: Maximum number of real-time jobs supported.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.supportedRtJobGps: Supported GPS intervals for real-time jobs.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.finalROP: Boolean indicating final ROP support.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.measurementJobSupport: Boolean indicating measurement job support.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.jobStartStopSupport: Level of support for job start/stop.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.supportedCompressionTypes: Supported compression types for PM files.
- PmMeasurementCapabilities.supportedThreshJobGps: Supported GPS intervals for threshold jobs.
